title: Ep - 177 - WHITNEY PORT FROM THE HILLS
description:
Whitney Port is a fashion designer, author, and a cast member on The Hills: New Beginnings on MTV. She discusses how she was cast for MTV’s original show, her experience on MTV’s The City, her experience filming Tyler Henry Hollywood Medium, and The Hills new reboot. 


Comedian Heather McDonald helps Kate review Bachelor in Paradise. 


Whitney Ward Dillon and Mariel Lane from CMT’s Racing Wives talk about the show, which centers on the lives of NASCAR’s most prominent wives, and the personal and professional demands they face.
